a while to redefine =E2=80=9Cworking from home.=E2=80=9D
</p>
<p style=3D"font-family:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rg=
b(51,51,51)">I=E2=80=99ve been location independent for 15 years, although =
far from what you would call a nomad. But as <a href=3D"https://click.conve=
