mily:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(190,129,0)" targe=
t=3D"_blank">we discussed a couple weeks ago</a>, my plan is to live in dif=
ferent parts of the world on a more-or-less permanent basis when my kids ar=
e out of high school.
</p>
<p style=3D"font-family:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rg=
b(51,51,51)">While I like to keep things on the positive tip, being unconst=
rained by geography has another aspect to it. I see it as a necessity at th=
is point that my family and I are not tied to any one country =E2=80=93=E2=
=80=93 the United States in particular.
</p>
<p style=3D"font-family:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rg=
b(51,51,51)">For years you=E2=80=99ve heard about the decline of the U.S., =
especially on the global leadership front. But the more pragmatic concern i=
s that <a href=3D"https://click.convertkit-mail2.com/4zu7pwv4elhehvxkk7sx/3=
