" style=3D"font-family:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb=
(190,129,0)" target=3D"_blank">the quality of life has dropped</a> in Ameri=
ca over the last decade, even as it has risen almost everywhere else.
</p>
<p style=3D"font-family:source-sans-pro,helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rg=
b(51,51,51)">Once the pandemic hit, many trends already in motion accelerat=
ed -- including the sentiment that things are going south in the States. Th=
is led Americans who can work virtually to <a href=3D"https://click.convert=
